Use a column chart stacked to 100 percent when you have multiple groupings and are interested in the proportions between values in each grouping, as well as each grouping's total.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

For example, to compare the number of opportunities created each month by campaign source in a report, set record count as the Y-axis, created month as the X-axis, and source as the Groupings value.
